ir and Vinod are framed for scams, which they had set out to expose, Shobha walks away from the duo leaving them to face the music. Characters talk incessantly either about corruption or about being corrupt. It went after civil engineering companies that continuously cheats while building bridges, roads, airports, dams, you name it. Jaane Bhi Do Yaaro (transl. This dark comedy has a compelling star cast encompassing Naseeruddin Shah, Om Puri, Ravi Baswani and Pankaj Kapur. Tag: Jaane Bhi Do Yaaro How Vidhu Vinod Chopra SMARTLY saves costs on his films is a MUST-READ for every big and small filmmaker in the country Jan 29, 2021 - 9:00 am IST Jaane Bhi Do Yaaro is Hindi cinema’s ultimate comedy film. Nothing can restore the austerity and begging-bowl crisis that the film had to face. The nation was not in the best of moods. All in all, Jaane Bhi Do Yaaro provides a string of images from Mumbai which provides a different reality of the city than what is usually portrayed in Hindi cinema. If you are a fan of comedy, there are chances you count the Bollywood classic, ‘Jaane Bhi Do Yaaro’ as one of your favourites. Coming to the storytelling choices, I am surprised that everybody has conveniently forgotten about the misogynistic undertones of Jaane Bhi Do Yaaron which are played off as gags. In addition to that, it managed to show the futility of fighting over what's right when the rich are dominating a major section of the narrative. Funnily enough, that has become the reality as a January report has shown that India's richest 1% are in control of 73% of the country's wealth, thereby controlling what's true and what's not via news, social media and more. Jaane Bhi Do Yaaro ( 6 ) IMDb 8.4 2h 11min 1983 ALL Two photographers, who are employed by a newspaper editor to expose the scandalous activities of the rich, come across corruption by a builder and accidentally photograph a murder. At the beginning of the film, Ravi Baswani's Sudhir Mishra openly harasses a girl in an a